title: Taymuraz Toboyev
text:
Taymuraz Muratovich Toboyev (; born 9 March 1995) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a>. He plays for <a href="FC%20Mashuk-KMV%20Pyatigorsk">Mashuk-KMV Pyatigorsk</a>.
Career.
Toboyev made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> for <a href="FC%20SKA-Energiya%20Khabarovsk">FC SKA-Energiya Khabarovsk</a> on 23 August 2013 in a game against <a href="FC%20Gazovik%20Orenburg">FC Gazovik Orenburg</a>.
On 26 June 2019, <a href="FC%20Ararat%20Yerevan">Ararat Yerevan</a> announced the signing of Toboyev, along with 12 other players, before leaving Ararat Yerevan on 16 January 2020.
On 4 February 2020, <a href="FC%20Urartu">Urartu</a> announced the signing of Toboyev. On 13 July 2020, Toboyev left Urartu by mutual agreement.
